org.bladerunnerjs.utility.reader

Class JsCodeBlockStrippingDependenciesReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.Reader
      • org.bladerunnerjs.utility.reader.JsCodeBlockStrippingDependenciesReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Readable

    public class JsCodeBlockStrippingDependenciesReader
extends java.io.Reader
    Strips the contents of function blocks when reading. NOTE: This should only be used when determining the dependencies of a class. It doesn't handle the removal of the start of the function block and will result in invalid JS.
